text: Ainaro is a municipality of East Timor. Its capital is the city of Ainaro. Ainaro has the highest point in East Timor, Mount Ramelau (2,960 m). ==Administrative posts== The municipality's administrative posts (formerly sub-districts) are: *Ainaro Administrative Post (place of capital) *Hato-Udo Administrative Post *Hatu-Builico Administrative Post *Maubisse Administrative Post == References == Category:Municipalities of East Timor
title: Ainaro Municipality
